<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ʿlmny yạ ạ̹lhy ạ̉sẖkr ʿly̱ ạldwạm
 ạ̉sẖkr mhmạ ykwn ạ̉sẖkr wsṭ ạlậlạm
